> Quick answer: collect your experience, 35 contact hours, and references first—**then** start the online form so you can finish it in one sitting.

## 1) Confirm Eligibility
- 4-year degree → 36 months leading projects  
- Secondary degree → 60 months leading projects  
- 35 Contact Hours required

## 2) Prepare Your Evidence
- Outcome-focused bullets
- Map to People / Process / Business Environment
- Keep consistent dates / roles

## 3) Create PMI Account
Professional email recommended.

## 4) Fill the Application Form
Describe scope/objectives/outcomes; use verbs like:
- led / facilitated / negotiated / prioritized

## 5) Review and Submit
Double-check dates/totals/contacts.

## 6) Audit (If Selected)
Prepare certificates and experience verification.

## 7) Schedule Exam
Book after you can score 75%+ on full mock exams.

